@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Concurenta TCP: un handler per client

rectangle "Thread principal\naccept loop" as MAIN

rectangle "Handler client A" as HA
rectangle "Handler client B" as HB
rectangle "Handler client C" as HC

MAIN --> HA : accept + dispatch
MAIN --> HB : accept + dispatch
MAIN --> HC : accept + dispatch

note bottom of MAIN
  Variante uzuale:
  - thread per client
  - process per client
  - async / event loop
end note
@enduml